ion Planning agent, skill, or Copilot Studio artifact to bring over\\n- Use that as the handoff into local development\",\"demo_actions\":\"- Land on the concrete next step\\n- Show the Production Planning agent, skill, or Copilot Studio artifact\\n- End on the handoff into code and agent development\"}]}",
